history.content:
https://acropolis.cs.berkeley.edu/~account/webacct/

Log in here, and you can see your accounts. The easiest thing to do is reset your account password for the machines, and then set them again.

You can also email yourself the account sheet.

I've already registered my account for the Soda computers, but I still haven't for Cory. How do I find out the original password(the one on the account sheet) for my CS account so I can register my account for the computers in Cory?
history.subject: how to get the original password for a cs class account?
